{"tid":687432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王嘉爾都被鬧「港獨」","createTime":"2018-06-02T09:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T12:22:38.000Z","uid":38671,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"571d3a8a1e6a70f072b4f1a38a650301d24a65c7","tid":687432,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:08:28.000Z","msg":"擦鞋又點, 自稱香港人就係罪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 韓國男團GOT7嘅香港成員Jackson（王嘉爾）喺大陸人氣高企，佢亦要中韓兩邊走，近日有網民就喺微博發表大量具有侮辱性嘅言論，指摘Jackson愛講大話，留言包括「港獨」、「廢物」、「死爹」等字眼。<br />\n<br />\nJackson方面因為被網民侮辱，其工作室噚晚就喺官方微博發表律師信，針對部份微博用戶喺網上發佈有關Jackson不當嘅言論，直指網民嚴重侵犯咗Jackson嘅名譽權，同時要求有關網民要刪除相關言論並作出道歉，又呼籲：「網路不是謠言的避風港，願共同維護和諧自由的網路環境。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180602/large/1527915857_8f8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180602%2Flarge%2F1527915857_8f8b.jpg&h=44fb02ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180602/large/1527916098_527a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180602%2Flarge%2F1527916098_527a.jpg&h=85629dc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180602/58268453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58268453&d=xD%2BGrjRUql2tyaiMwagBQTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f1fabbbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58268453&h=dc082032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180602/58268453</a>"},{"pid":"b8778187357fc99