aces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只要你唔係姓黨<br />\n過左隨機時間就屈你港獨"},{"pid":"32aa4194d32634abaad450303ee6bc374298155e","tid":687432,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果依條友咁都可以比人講到係港獨, 大陸啲香港藝人應該可以全部收皮"},{"pid":"07440fb3ca21bf9cbdc863a304468a4d00d77a4c","tid":687432,"uid":53811,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:16:24.000Z","msg":"個個大陸後生都係紅衛兵血統<br />\n心血來潮就塞條罪比你嘆<br />\n理得你奶到狗都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cab6277780a1147a41f77e00b229f80dc0bf1cd","tid":687432,"uid":37808,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:22:38.000Z","msg":"啲大陸仔冇撚腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  國籍唔寫香港寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  過關寫中國俾人問長問短<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}